<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0701a" n="0701a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701a02"/><div1 type="xu"><mulu type="序" level="1" label="No. 1312-A 通玄百問序"/><head>No. 1312-A
<lb ed="X" n="0701a03"/> 通玄百問序</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0701a04"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701a05"/><p id="pX67p0701a0501">聞&CB06702;山正&CB00160;。迦葉親承。少室真風。神光立受。自六傳
<lb ed="X" n="0701a06"/>之後。五派以來。法雷聲震於中州。佛日光流於上苑。
<lb ed="X" n="0701a07"/>其有雲仍種草者矣。圓通著百問。激勵學徒。闡一心
<lb ed="X" n="0701a08"/>弘持祖道。其言簡當。其旨幽微。寧容紙背上參求。那
<lb ed="X" n="0701a09"/>許口角頭取辨。若非偉器。難搆洪機。</p><p id="pX67p0701a0915" place="inline">當時未遇其人。
<lb ed="X" n="0701a10"/>過日方逢作者。故萬松老師居摩訶菩提蘭若。運三
<lb ed="X" n="0701a11"/>昧正受神通。傳法之餘。匡持之暇。答前百問於指頃。
<lb ed="X" n="0701a12"/>誘後群迷於目今。眼埵陬活C臨濟機縱橫得玅。舌頭
<lb ed="X" n="0701a13"/>無骨。雲門語左右逢源。不拘悟本偏圓。靡定清&CB00289;得
<lb ed="X" n="0701a14"/>失。多字學。徒知費力。如人拜。足忍疲勞。</p><p id="pX67p0701a1416" place="inline">腦後另具鉗
<lb ed="X" n="0701a15"/>鎚。舌本別存鑪&CB02021;。圓通之問。萬松之訓。可謂盡善矣。
<lb ed="X" n="0701a16"/>故不撥。從倫偶依是錄。謾述浮詞。非唯無補宗乘。抑
<lb ed="X" n="0701a17"/>亦濫叨祖域。頌之過半。會公澤唱之於前。錄之逮畢。
<lb ed="X" n="0701a18"/>永叔能和之於後。累及二老。取笑諸方。要知終始。狂
<lb ed="X" n="0701a19"/>情讀誦。向下註&CB00560;。叢林閑散幾經秋。宗教通搜未有
<lb ed="X" n="0701a20"/>由。愚魯自慚空過日。忍將狐尾補貂裘。&CB00364;申是意。聊
<lb ed="X" n="0701a21"/>為序云。&CB13808;逢執除七夕前二日龍巖林泉顯道序。</p></div1>
<lb ed="X" n="0701a22"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701a23"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701a24"/>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0701b" n="0701b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b01"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b02"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b03"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b04"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b05"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="通玄百問"/><head type="no">No. 1312</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead>通玄百問</jhead></juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b07"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b08"/><byline type="other">玉溪通玄庵圓通大禪師設問</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b09"/><byline type="other">摩訶菩提蘭若萬松和尚仰答</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b10"/><byline type="other">龍嚴林泉老人頌</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b11"/><byline type="other">華亭生生道人梓</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701b1201">問。行玄猶是涉崎嶇。如何是平坦處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701b1215" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。東西南北。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b13"/><p id="pX67p0701b1301" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。東西南北。侵天荊棘。沒足石人。不消勞力。更須
<lb ed="X" n="0701b14"/>透過那重關。自在縱橫方脫纏。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701b1501">問。玄玄玄處亦須呵。且道有甚麼過。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701b1515" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。罪不重科。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b16"/><p id="pX67p0701b1601" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。罪不重科。閑管多羅。未語<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>前早錯。那堪變態
<lb ed="X" n="0701b17"/>&CB05070;訛。阿呵呵。玄與玄玄爭甚麼。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701b1801">問。一花百億國。且道一花在甚麼處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701b1815" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。不風流處
<lb ed="X" n="0701b19"/>也風流。</p><p id="pX67p0701b1904" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。不風流處也風流。無蒂花開鐵樹頭。伶
<lb ed="X" n="0701b20"/>俐禪和高著眼。非同春色媚皇州。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701b2101">問。炎天似火。暑雨如湯。正當此時。如何迴避。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701b2118" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。主
<lb ed="X" n="0701b22"/>山前。案山後。</p><p id="pX67p0701b2206" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。主山前。案山後。日午面南看北斗。
<lb ed="X" n="0701b23"/>騰騰炎暑任遷流。畢竟難侵無相叟。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701b24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701b2401">問。大海為墨。須彌為筆。且道寫箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701b2416" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。通玄百
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0701c" n="0701c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c01"/>問。</p><p id="pX67p0701c0102" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。通玄百問。不拘音韻。縱奪臨時。各安其分。有
<lb ed="X" n="0701c02"/>人問我若奚為。文彩縱橫看變運。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c03"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701c0301">問。園媃[花。一悟真如。今觀花也。還有悟真底麼。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c04"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701c0401" rend="margin-left:1em">答。試問東君也不知。</p><p id="pX67p0701c0409" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。試問東君也不知。不知底
<lb ed="X" n="0701c05"/>事果何為。聾於鼻孔纔堪聽。瞎似眉毛方可窺。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701c0601">問。萬物推遷。還有不推遷底麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701c0613" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。住岸&CB00230;迷人。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c07"/><p id="pX67p0701c0701" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。住岸&CB00230;迷人。真語亦真。龍樓無宿客。鳳閣有朝
<lb ed="X" n="0701c08"/>臣。薦取玄中旨。誇足下塵。欲窮親切處。九盡又逢
<lb ed="X" n="0701c09"/>春。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701c1001">問。四時改變。還有不改變底麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701c1013" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。春寒秋熱。</p><p id="pX67p0701c1018" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0701c11"/>春寒秋熱。年年不別。碧海纖塵。紅鑪片雪。霜餘葉
<lb ed="X" n="0701c12"/>落樹元閑。雨過雲收天愈潔。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701c1301">問。尋師訪道為參禪。祗如禪作麼生參。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701c1316" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。久嚮道
<lb ed="X" n="0701c14"/>風。</p><p id="pX67p0701c1402" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。久嚮道風。理事雙融。言言般若。物物圓通。其
<lb ed="X" n="0701c15"/>或蹉過當頭句。且向嵩陽問祖翁。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c16"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701c1601">問。溈山水牯牛向甚麼處放。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701c1612" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。烏那青青處。</p><p id="pX67p0701c1618" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0701c17"/>烏那青青處。斫額應難&CB15111;。更擬問如何。&CB15143;過新羅
<lb ed="X" n="0701c18"/>去。牧&CB00594;高歌唱月歸。鼻頭繩斷元無據。吽。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c19"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701c1901">問。德山是佛祖兒孫。為甚麼佛來也打。祖來也打。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c20"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701c2001" rend="margin-left:1em">答。不敢怠慢。</p><p id="pX67p0701c2006" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。不敢怠慢。叢林頗慣。知恩報恩。心
<lb ed="X" n="0701c21"/>心無間。雲門正令肯提持。管取河清并海晏。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0701c2201">問。臨濟是佛祖苗裔。為甚麼佛來也喝。祖來也喝。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0701c23"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0701c2301" rend="margin-left:1em">答。祇為佛來祖來。</p><p id="pX67p0701c2308" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。佛來祖來。切忌胡猜。吾今為
<lb ed="X" n="0701c24"/>汝。十字轟開。苟或未委真消息。更聽忽雷震九垓。
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0702a" n="0702a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a01"/>咄。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a0201">問。趙州指&CB00177;。靈鷲拈花。且道是同是別。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a0216" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。&CB00594;兩指。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a03"/><p id="pX67p0702a0301" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB00594;兩指。立綱紀。付全提。而<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>矣。正休節外強生
<lb ed="X" n="0702a04"/>枝。莫認浮華并浪&CB00610;。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a0501">問。洞山無寒暑處甚麼人受用。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a0513" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。嘉州石像。</p><p id="pX67p0702a0518" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0702a06"/>嘉州石像。眉橫眼上。逼塞&CB00980;空。無偏無黨。賞心樂
<lb ed="X" n="0702a07"/>事許多般。何用銜花來供養。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a0801">問。直須登徹妙高峰。祇如妙高峰作麼生登。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a0818" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。有
<lb ed="X" n="0702a09"/>勞法重。</p><p id="pX67p0702a0904" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。有勞法重。當人變弄。妙握吹毛。萬邦一
<lb ed="X" n="0702a10"/>統。不涉纖塵歷大千。須知無用成真用。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a1101">問。明與無明。其性無二。如何是無二之性。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a1117" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。天曉
<lb ed="X" n="0702a12"/>不露。</p><p id="pX67p0702a1203" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。天曉不露。龍吟宿霧。語忌十成。機貴回互。
<lb ed="X" n="0702a13"/>滄海曦輪欲吐光。無端還被輕煙&CB00107;。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a14"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a1401">問。一超直入如來地。作麼生說箇超底道理。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a1418" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。抱
<lb ed="X" n="0702a15"/>瓮之流。</p><p id="pX67p0702a1504" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。抱瓮之流。豈貴良謀。始信清貪常樂。方
<lb ed="X" n="0702a16"/>知濁富多憂。&CB06401;。&CB06401;。&CB06401;。得抽頭處且抽頭。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a1701">問。般若無知。為甚麼無所不知。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a1713" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。莫謗他好。</p><p id="pX67p0702a1718" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0702a18"/>莫謗他好。巧說不如直道。但能語絕幽玄。便見心
<lb ed="X" n="0702a19"/>非做造。兀兀騰騰信自如。&CB02098;前落葉從風掃。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a20"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a2001">問。明&CB13122;下安排。且道安排箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a2014" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。適來新到。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a21"/><p id="pX67p0702a2101" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。適來新到。妙通玄奧。把纜放船。相頭買帽。若非
<lb ed="X" n="0702a22"/>佛日顯&CB15109;懷。夾嶺門庭孰可造。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a23"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702a2301">問。長安雖&CB00436;。我國晏然。如何是我國。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702a2315" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。正&CB00436;在。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0702a24"/><p id="pX67p0702a2401" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。正&CB00436;在。明眼宗師無&CB07724;礙。坐看喧靜與興亡。掌
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0702b" n="0702b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b01"/>握乾坤彰聖代。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b0201">問。摩騰未來此土。還有教也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b0213" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。待無即道。</p><p id="pX67p0702b0218" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0702b03"/>待無即道。探竿影草。白馬&CB02098;前。立分&CB00034;稻。貝葉靈
<lb ed="X" n="0702b04"/>文絕古今。莫隨言句生憂腦。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b0501">問。達磨未來此土。還有禪也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b0513" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。待有即道。</p><p id="pX67p0702b0518" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0702b06"/>待有即道。聲光浩浩。莫錯商量。休別尋討。休尋討。
<lb ed="X" n="0702b07"/>柳梢畢竟無酸棗。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b0801">問。沒底船子為甚麼無漏堅固。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b0813" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。生鐵鑄成。</p><p id="pX67p0702b0818" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0702b09"/>生鐵鑄成。非重非輕。無漏堅固。來往縱橫。不涉波
<lb ed="X" n="0702b10"/>瀾遊性海。五濁惡世度眾生。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b1101">問。鹽官犀牛扇子分付與恁麼人。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b1114" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>承厚意。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b12"/><p id="pX67p0702b1201" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>承厚意。斯言可記。開口廝當。豈容擬議。停待
<lb ed="X" n="0702b13"/>兮明月當天。動轉兮清風&CB00038;地。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b14"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b1401">問。趙州七觔布衫多年。還破碎也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b1415" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。一回拈出
<lb ed="X" n="0702b15"/>一回新。</p><p id="pX67p0702b1504" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。一回拈出一回新。信手拈來用最親。百
<lb ed="X" n="0702b16"/>二十年提掇畢。至今依舊不離身。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b1701">問。泥牛吼月。甚麼人得聞。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b1711" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。癩漢眉毛。</p><p id="pX67p0702b1716" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。癩漢
<lb ed="X" n="0702b18"/>眉毛果解聞。須彌驚起夜乘雲。知音不必頻頻舉。
<lb ed="X" n="0702b19"/>八兩分明是半觔。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b20"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b2001">問。木馬嘶聲。阿誰解聽。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b2010" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。徒勞拭眥。</p><p id="pX67p0702b2015" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。徒勞拭
<lb ed="X" n="0702b21"/>眥向空聽。萬籟聲騰本自寧。察理聆音休費力。雨
<lb ed="X" n="0702b22"/>餘依舊數峰青。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b23"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702b2301">問。三&CB00560;驢子弄蹄行。且道日行多少。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702b2315" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。莫亂走。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0702b24"/><p id="pX67p0702b2401" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。莫亂走。落草之談誰不有。更休特地問前程。擬
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0702c" n="0702c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c01"/>議思量成過咎。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c0201">問。無角鐵牛眠少室。且道有甚麼用處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c0216" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。卑不動
<lb ed="X" n="0702c03"/>尊。</p><p id="pX67p0702c0302" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。卑不動尊。道理須存。下不測上。誰敢言論。無
<lb ed="X" n="0702c04"/>陰陽地非關涉。杜撰農夫枉斷魂。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c0501">問。雖成佛道。不捨因門。且道為甚麼如此。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c0517" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。一串
<lb ed="X" n="0702c06"/>穿&CB00230;。</p><p id="pX67p0702c0603" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。一串穿&CB00230;。許多落索。細細思量。&CB00001;&CB00001;卜度。
<lb ed="X" n="0702c07"/>&CB06401;卜度。黑是寒鴉白是&CB15112;。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c0801">問。諸佛不出世。為甚麼&CB00230;向王宮生。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c0815" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。青山常舉
<lb ed="X" n="0702c09"/>足。</p><p id="pX67p0702c0902" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。青山常舉足。五目應難矚。不是大周遮。為非
<lb ed="X" n="0702c10"/>同世俗。同世俗。縱橫在欲而無欲。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c1101">問。亦無有涅槃。為甚麼&CB00230;向雙林滅。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c1115" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。白日不移
<lb ed="X" n="0702c12"/>輪。</p><p id="pX67p0702c1202" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。白日不移輪。潛通劫外春。莫貪尋旦暮。昧&CB00230;
<lb ed="X" n="0702c13"/>本來人。本來人。觸處居塵不染塵。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c14"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c1401">問。達磨西來。不立文字。為甚麼道金剛．楞伽是吾心
<lb ed="X" n="0702c15"/>要。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c1502" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。賴是心要。</p><p id="pX67p0702c1507" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。賴是心要。勦絕玄妙。突透禪
<lb ed="X" n="0702c16"/>關。通天一竅。誰知碧眼老胡僧。至今猶惹傍人笑。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c1701">問。二祖&CB00697;心了不可得。為甚麼&CB00230;道我自調心。非關
<lb ed="X" n="0702c18"/>汝事。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c1803" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。莫閑管。</p><p id="pX67p0702c1807" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。莫閑管。大似裁長聊補短。三
<lb ed="X" n="0702c19"/>星片月本無形。何勞特地生希罕。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c20"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c2001">問。般若說二十空。如何揀擇。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c2012" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。不多不少。</p><p id="pX67p0702c2017" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。不
<lb ed="X" n="0702c21"/>多不少。明明了了。三祖有言。諸人可曉。至道無難
<lb ed="X" n="0702c22"/>一句親。大慈千手難魔嬈。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c23"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0702c2301">問。金剛四相．圓覺四相。是同是別。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0702c2314" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。隔系不灸病。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0702c24"/><p id="pX67p0702c2401" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。隔系不灸病。老盧摠權柄。縱奪在臨時。諸人看
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0703a" n="0703a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a01"/>性命。鐵騎禪和不必爭。近來四海清如鏡。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a0201">問。楞嚴二十五圓通。那箇最親切。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a0214" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。好客無&CB00520;伴。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a03"/><p id="pX67p0703a0301" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。好客無&CB00520;伴。不消重判斷。南山共北山。氣勢俱
<lb ed="X" n="0703a04"/>摩漢。明月與陰雲。愛憎人眾半。妍&CB05554;任彼分。吾道
<lb ed="X" n="0703a05"/>一以貫。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a0601">問。步步登高易。甚麼處最高。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a0612" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。大洋海底。</p><p id="pX67p0703a0617" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。大
<lb ed="X" n="0703a07"/>洋海底。爭參祖禰。恰與別峰。不爭半米。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a0801">問。心心放下難。如何是放下底人。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a0814" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。擔取去。</p><p id="pX67p0703a0818" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0703a09"/>擔取去。最是趙州親切處。滿&CB00425;盛來一物無。莫隨
<lb ed="X" n="0703a10"/>狂妄生憂慮。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a1101">問。楊岐金剛圈甚麼人透得。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a1112" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。過。</p><p id="pX67p0703a1114" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。過。這些關
<lb ed="X" n="0703a12"/>捩天來大。電光石火薦還遲。不免被他親勘破。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a1301">問。楊岐栗棘蓬。甚麼人吞得。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a1312" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。了。</p><p id="pX67p0703a1314" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。了。妙用神
<lb ed="X" n="0703a14"/>通非小小。佛殿燈籠更互容。此時未審何人曉。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a1501">問。還有過得黃龍三關底麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a1512" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。除非和尚。</p><p id="pX67p0703a1517" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。除
<lb ed="X" n="0703a16"/>非和尚。當仁不讓。萬世規模。十方榜樣。佛手驢&CB00560;
<lb ed="X" n="0703a17"/>兮胡用他求。彼我生緣兮應須自向。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a1801">問。喝一喝。云。且道是賓是主。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a1812" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。賓主歷然。</p><p id="pX67p0703a1817" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。當
<lb ed="X" n="0703a19"/>時照用曾施設。正法眼藏瞎驢滅。主伴交參向上
<lb ed="X" n="0703a20"/>機。知音不必重甄別。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a2101">問。&CB00594;起拂子云。為你說禪了也。作麼生會。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703a2117" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。今日
<lb ed="X" n="0703a22"/>不著便。</p><p id="pX67p0703a2204" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。今日不著便。大似埋兵還掉戰。大唐打
<lb ed="X" n="0703a23"/>破尚難求。唯要阿師通一線。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703a24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703a2401">問。拈起拄杖云。還有向拄杖頭上下得一轉語底麼。</p></sp>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0703b" n="0703b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b01"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703b0101" rend="margin-left:1em">答。和尚年尊。</p><p id="pX67p0703b0106" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。年尊妙語足超情。不動干戈定
<lb ed="X" n="0703b02"/>太平。紫鷰黃鸝&CB06401;巧語。大音須信果希聲。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b03"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703b0301">問。畫一圓相。云。三世諸佛．六代祖師總在堻\。作麼
<lb ed="X" n="0703b04"/>生會。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703b0403" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。宿生慶幸。</p><p id="pX67p0703b0408" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。宿生慶幸。日煖月冷。四海
<lb ed="X" n="0703b05"/>收波。乾坤肅靜。欽師猶被馬師惑。直至如今猶未
<lb ed="X" n="0703b06"/>省。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b07"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703b0701">問。以手空中點一點。云。且道這一點。明甚麼邊事。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b08"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703b0801" rend="margin-left:1em">答。歸宗猶在。</p><p id="pX67p0703b0806" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。歸宗猶在。兩彩一賽。這畔無妨。那
<lb ed="X" n="0703b09"/>邊不礙。永書八法好生看。先輩當年曾下載。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703b1001">問。行不出戶。坐不當堂底人。汝等還識麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703b1017" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。滄洲
<lb ed="X" n="0703b11"/>短尾龍。</p><p id="pX67p0703b1104" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。滄洲短尾龍。夭矯若寒松。不借葉公筆。
<lb ed="X" n="0703b12"/>寧拘葛氏筇。當堂無朕跡。&CB00642;界露形容。擬涉思量
<lb ed="X" n="0703b13"/>處。千峰與萬峰。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b14"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703b1401">問。撒手那邊底人。為甚麼不居正位。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703b1415" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。大功不宰。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b15"/><p id="pX67p0703b1501" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。大功不宰。聲光猶在。踢倒涅槃床。踏翻寂滅海。
<lb ed="X" n="0703b16"/>把住放行兮觸處自由。奪正縱偏兮有勞神彩。但
<lb ed="X" n="0703b17"/>能就路還家。日者徒占戌亥。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703b1801">問。回頭這畔底人。為甚麼不墮偏方。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703b1815" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。至化無為。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b19"/><p id="pX67p0703b1901" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。至化無為。闔國稱奇。清風來紫塞。皓月印丹墀。
<lb ed="X" n="0703b20"/>即理之事兮元非有間。即俗之真兮本不相離。自
<lb ed="X" n="0703b21"/>從一證無師智。遶&CB00642;閻浮足不移。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703b22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703b2201">問。七縱八橫。千變萬化底人。為甚麼正合喫棒。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703b2219" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0703b23"/>幾乎放過。</p><p id="pX67p0703b2305" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。幾乎放過付全提。妙用宜施果必奇。
<lb ed="X" n="0703b24"/>見義不為無勇也。知恩方報乃忠之。好看狹路泥
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0703c" n="0703c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c01"/>中<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">刺</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">剌</rdg></app>。善保&CB00980;囊橐媕@。若遇頑嚚無血漢。方知鈍
<lb ed="X" n="0703c02"/>鐵費鉗鎚。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c03"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703c0301">問。百了千當底人。將甚麼賞他。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703c0313" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。趙州茶。曹山酒。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c04"/><p id="pX67p0703c0401" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。趙州茶。曹山酒。不須烹醞時時有。渴來何礙兩
<lb ed="X" n="0703c05"/>三杯。醒後無妨七八斗。未了區區陪奉伊。恐隨&CB01003;
<lb ed="X" n="0703c06"/>味徒開口。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c07"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703c0701">問。風穴對五點。那點最親。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703c0711" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。此點最親。</p><p id="pX67p0703c0716" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。此點
<lb ed="X" n="0703c08"/>最親。心真語真。爍開衲僧鼻孔。增新佛祖精神。建
<lb ed="X" n="0703c09"/>法幢於實際。立宗旨於纖塵。識情卜度知無數。直
<lb ed="X" n="0703c10"/>下全通有幾人。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703c1101">問。雲門垂三句語。那句最妙。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703c1112" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。此句最妙。</p><p id="pX67p0703c1117" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。此
<lb ed="X" n="0703c12"/>句最妙。一言便了。莫逐是非。人間擾擾。禪流著意
<lb ed="X" n="0703c13"/>細參詳。此上神通非小小。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c14"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703c1401">問。佛不說一字。為甚麼教滿龍宮。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703c1414" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。二字三字。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c15"/><p id="pX67p0703c1501" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。二字三字。是義非義。般若真源。無師妙智。止啼
<lb ed="X" n="0703c16"/>黃葉好生看。剔起眉毛休擬議。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703c1701">問。因該果海。果徹因源。祇如離&CB00230;因果一句作麼生
<lb ed="X" n="0703c18"/>道。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703c1802" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。道也未道。</p><p id="pX67p0703c1807" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。道也未道。不須尋討。因語識
<lb ed="X" n="0703c19"/>人。從苗辨草。了四諦兮不必商量。超十地兮未敢
<lb ed="X" n="0703c20"/>相保。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0703c2101">問。小始終頓圓。五教中還有禪也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0703c2115" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。識教也未。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0703c22"/><p id="pX67p0703c2201" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。識教也未超情謂。擬別商量。楊湯止沸。銀漢浪
<lb ed="X" n="0703c23"/>兮雖分。瓊林花兮不異。異不異。明眼衲僧&CB06401;觸
<lb ed="X" n="0703c24"/>諱。</p></sp></dialog>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0704a" n="0704a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a01"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704a0101">問。向道莫去。歸來背父。如何得不背父去。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704a0117" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。切忌
<lb ed="X" n="0704a02"/>回頭。</p><p id="pX67p0704a0203" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。切忌回頭一句奇。箇中玄奧幾人知。但能
<lb ed="X" n="0704a03"/>足下無私去。鳥道縱橫觸處宜。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a04"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704a0401">問。隨緣赴感靡不周。而痝B此菩提座。且道那堿O
<lb ed="X" n="0704a05"/>菩提座。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704a0504" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。不是即道。</p><p id="pX67p0704a0509" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。不是即道。幸勿草草。瓦
<lb ed="X" n="0704a06"/>礫荊榛。無非至寶。妙體絕依一句玄。剎塵等&CB00642;瞿
<lb ed="X" n="0704a07"/>曇老。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704a0801">問。菩提妙花&CB00642;莊嚴。隨所住處常安樂。那堿O菩提
<lb ed="X" n="0704a09"/>妙華。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704a0903" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。賣盡風流不著錢。</p><p id="pX67p0704a0911" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。賣盡風流不著錢。
<lb ed="X" n="0704a10"/>知音不必更重宣。空生見慣尋常也。餓眼禪和更
<lb ed="X" n="0704a11"/>可怜。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704a1201">問。聞鐘登寶殿。擊鼓上&CB00980;空。莫是觀音入理之門麼。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a13"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704a1301" rend="margin-left:1em">答。低聲。低聲。</p><p id="pX67p0704a1306" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。低聲舉似不&CB05070;訛。無恨勞生會
<lb ed="X" n="0704a14"/>也麼。悲智願心澄海月。聞思脩慧引風柯。杜禪和。
<lb ed="X" n="0704a15"/>莫蹉跎。隨聲逐色果如何。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a16"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704a1601">問。絕情解。透聲色。明心見性底人還徹也未。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704a1618" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。&CB00424;
<lb ed="X" n="0704a17"/>在不疑之地。</p><p id="pX67p0704a1706" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB00424;在不疑之地。迷悟是非一致。當
<lb ed="X" n="0704a18"/>年潦倒玄沙。曾被靈雲返戲。你誇了了明明。我道
<lb ed="X" n="0704a19"/>儼然瞌睡。休瞌睡。雨餘雲霽山添翠。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a20"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704a2001">問。生如著衫。死如脫&CB01726;底人。得箇甚麼道理。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704a2018" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。赤
<lb ed="X" n="0704a21"/>手空拳。</p><p id="pX67p0704a2104" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。赤手空拳事事無。更須放下復迴途。若
<lb ed="X" n="0704a22"/>能如是承當去。方信闍黎德不孤。德不孤。莫含胡。
<lb ed="X" n="0704a23"/>&CB06401;&CB00295;萬子人皆有。祇恐臨時不丈夫。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704a24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704a2401">問。過去<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>滅。未來未至。現在空寂。&CB00230;為甚麼逆順境
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0704b" n="0704b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b01"/>界現前時便透不得。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b0109" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。&CB00230;知痛痒。</p><p id="pX67p0704b0114" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB00230;知痛痒。
<lb ed="X" n="0704b02"/>不辭提獎。昨夢初醒。是非<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>往。佛祖權橫在萬松。
<lb ed="X" n="0704b03"/>莫隨言句空勞攘。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b04"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704b0401">問。多聞捨無義。多聞解了法。且道解箇甚麼法。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b0419" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0704b05"/>此義文長。</p><p id="pX67p0704b0505" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。此義文長。切忌商量。不比蠅鑽故紙。
<lb ed="X" n="0704b06"/>豈同&CB00541;禦殘章。伶俐漢。莫荒唐。千手大悲難摸&CB01857;。
<lb ed="X" n="0704b07"/>無言童子善敷揚。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704b0801">問。我有一句子。明盡十玄門六相義。還有人道得麼。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b09"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b0901" rend="margin-left:1em">答。&CB01495;。</p><p id="pX67p0704b0903" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB01495;。截斷眾流。三玄三要。無比無儔。菊花
<lb ed="X" n="0704b10"/>開日重陽至。一葉落時天下秋。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704b1101">問。不住化城。直至寶所。且道那堿O寶所。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b1117" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。此處
<lb ed="X" n="0704b12"/>無金二兩。</p><p id="pX67p0704b1205" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。此處無金二兩。大似揚聲止響。衣珠
<lb ed="X" n="0704b13"/>歷歷分明。祇管玲竮飄蕩。若渠更擬不知處。便與
<lb ed="X" n="0704b14"/>攔腮轟一掌。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704b1501">問。凡所有相。皆是&CB00980;妄。那箇是真實底。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b1516" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。莫妄想
<lb ed="X" n="0704b16"/>好。</p><p id="pX67p0704b1602" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。莫妄想好。更無做造。要知真妄圓融。識取菩
<lb ed="X" n="0704b17"/>提煩惱。貪嗔痴。無非道。筭來枉了別尋討。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704b1801">問。一切有身。悉皆不淨。三十二相又作麼生。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b1818" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。打
<lb ed="X" n="0704b19"/>破畫瓶。</p><p id="pX67p0704b1904" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。打破畫瓶。猶醉忽醒。金身丈六。應物標
<lb ed="X" n="0704b20"/>形。秋水淨如僧眼碧。曉山濃似佛頭青。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704b2101">問。禪分五派。還有優劣也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b2112" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。劣則總劣。</p><p id="pX67p0704b2117" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。劣
<lb ed="X" n="0704b22"/>則總劣。不可分別。缾盤釵釧。體同名別。早是圓通
<lb ed="X" n="0704b23"/>多口。那堪仰嶠饒舌。為君決。六月日頭到處熱。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704b24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704b2401">問。教列三乘。還有勝負也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704b2412" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。勝則俱勝。</p><p id="pX67p0704b2417" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。勝
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0704c" n="0704c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c01"/>則俱勝。為渠親證。佛祖權衡。是定非定。雖然不與
<lb ed="X" n="0704c02"/>汝同槃。斤兩到頭難昧秤。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c03"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704c0301">問。性相二宗還有淺深也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704c0312" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。索另者先窮。</p><p id="pX67p0704c0318" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0704c04"/>索另先窮人盡知。圓融行布強支離。同田分貝君
<lb ed="X" n="0704c05"/>看取。家不和兮鄰里欺。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704c0601">問。作止任滅。四病如何醫治。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704c0612" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。右件各等分。</p><p id="pX67p0704c0618" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0704c07"/>右件各等分。感承垂寶訓。一丸療病安。何假驢般
<lb ed="X" n="0704c08"/>運。日面月面酬時。孰怕重重詢問。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704c0901">問。唯一月真。中間更無是月非月。如何是真月。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704c0919" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0704c10"/>清光何處無。</p><p id="pX67p0704c1006" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。清光何處無。妙德轉玄樞。穆穆金
<lb ed="X" n="0704c11"/>波冷。停停玉兔孤。曲&CB00424;猶不似。明鏡轉差殊。若會
<lb ed="X" n="0704c12"/>雲岩舉&CB00416;意。須知元不費功夫。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704c1301">問。維摩默然談不二。後代如何為舉揚。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704c1316" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。謝師點
<lb ed="X" n="0704c14"/>破。</p><p id="pX67p0704c1402" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。謝師點破。二俱話墮。誰想今朝又添一箇。如
<lb ed="X" n="0704c15"/>斯舉唱宗乘。笑殺東村王大。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c16"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704c1601">問。佛語心為宗。未審心以何為宗。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704c1614" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。何所不宗。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c17"/><p id="pX67p0704c1701" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。何所不宗。物物皆從。圓證一念。妙德顒顒。總似
<lb ed="X" n="0704c18"/>常啼渾賣&CB00230;。須知死水不藏龍。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c19"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704c1901">問。無門為法門。且道作麼生入。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704c1913" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。誰在門外。</p><p id="pX67p0704c1918" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0704c20"/>誰在門外。乾坤非大。圓覺伽藍。久經淘汰。不必&CB00234;
<lb ed="X" n="0704c21"/>筇月下敲。化城打破無遮礙。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0704c22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0704c2201">問。記一箇元字&CB00560;在心。作野狐精。祇如無元字&CB00560;。作
<lb ed="X" n="0704c23"/>箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0704c2304" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。更有赤鬚狐。</p><p id="pX67p0704c2310" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。更有赤鬚狐。哀哉肘
<lb ed="X" n="0704c24"/>後符。識情如實有。因果不&CB00980;無。巧若拙。智如愚。幾
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0705a" n="0705a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a01"/>箇男兒是丈夫。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705a0201">問。道箇佛法兩字。淨漱口三日。且道佛法過在甚麼
<lb ed="X" n="0705a03"/>處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705a0302" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。但喫吐而唾。</p><p id="pX67p0705a0308" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。但喫吐而唾。幾人窺得破。
<lb ed="X" n="0705a04"/>摩訶修多羅。南無三滿哆。三滿哆。言滿天下無口
<lb ed="X" n="0705a05"/>過。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705a0601">問。祖師教外別傳句。試請禪人吐露看。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705a0616" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。摩訶羅
<lb ed="X" n="0705a07"/>骨朵。</p><p id="pX67p0705a0703" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。摩訶羅骨朵。未肯全許可。立雪與拈花。曾
<lb ed="X" n="0705a08"/><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>遭&CB01333;&CB01334;。眉毛不惜報君知。熱則&CB01904;涼寒向火。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705a0901">問。石頭路滑人難過。碧玉溪邊作麼行。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705a0916" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。拈起拄
<lb ed="X" n="0705a10"/>杖。</p><p id="pX67p0705a1002" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。拈起拄杖。徐行而往。乾闥城中。毗盧頂上。石
<lb ed="X" n="0705a11"/>頭路滑兮非功。玉溪路曠兮絕想。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705a1201">問。喜得山中住。閑眠夢不驚。且道夢見箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705a1219" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0705a13"/>&CB06401;&CB00895;語。</p><p id="pX67p0705a1304" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB06401;&CB00895;語。華胥國破無依所。香嚴寂子太
<lb ed="X" n="0705a14"/>含胡。供水過茶祈&CB04676;許。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705a1501">問。雲居云。居山好。且道那堿O好處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705a1515" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。通玄峰頂。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a16"/><p id="pX67p0705a1601" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。通玄峰頂。天然孤&CB00529;。擬涉途程。鞭折汝脛。大隱
<lb ed="X" n="0705a17"/>居&CB04622;小隱山。隨人變運俱無等。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705a1801">問。吾師雨花外。不下十餘年。祇在此山中作箇甚麼。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a19"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705a1901" rend="margin-left:1em">答。有年無德。</p><p id="pX67p0705a1906" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。有年無德。不拘軌則。指東為西。
<lb ed="X" n="0705a20"/>呼南作北。祇麼窮通然較些。正眼觀來猶費力。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705a21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705a2101">問。此時山僧都不會。是會了不會。是不會不會。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705a2119" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0705a22"/>師會也未。</p><p id="pX67p0705a2205" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。師會也未。弄粥飯氣。妙轉天輪地軸。
<lb ed="X" n="0705a23"/>密織文經武緯。大璞不琢兮純真。圓珠不穴兮愈
<lb ed="X" n="0705a24"/>貴。</p></sp></dialog>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0705b" n="0705b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b01"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b0101">問。非知之艱。行之唯難。且道作麼生行。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b0116" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。請師先
<lb ed="X" n="0705b02"/>進。</p><p id="pX67p0705b0202" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。請師先進。不存逆順。&CB06401;問破危成收。莫說吉
<lb ed="X" n="0705b03"/>凶悔吝。大道縱橫本自平。何須腰佩空王印。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b04"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b0401">問。未達法源。故多諍論。還有達徹法源底麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b0418" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。掀
<lb ed="X" n="0705b05"/>倒蒲團。</p><p id="pX67p0705b0504" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。掀倒蒲團闡大機。幾人於此造玄微。法
<lb ed="X" n="0705b06"/>源窮徹無餘底。陡覺&CB00980;空減帶圍。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b07"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b0701">問。明明不昧。了了常知底。是箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b0715" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。鬼眼睛。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b08"/><p id="pX67p0705b0801" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。好箇英靈鬼眼睛。是非窺盡沒輸<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">贏</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">羸</rdg></app>。爭如兀兀
<lb ed="X" n="0705b09"/>無知去。且與眉稜結弟兄。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b1001">問。佛性與法性如何分別。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b1011" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。別日再商量。</p><p id="pX67p0705b1017" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。別
<lb ed="X" n="0705b11"/>日再商量。慈悲為舉揚。眉毛猶不惜。意路豈遮藏。
<lb ed="X" n="0705b12"/>夜月光連水。朝曦影轉廊。玉溪垂示處。細細好參
<lb ed="X" n="0705b13"/>詳。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b14"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b1401">問。遠行與順行。且道作麼生辨。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b1413" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。還有眼麼。</p><p id="pX67p0705b1418" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0705b15"/>還有眼麼。一言包裹。了了明明。箭穿紅垛。聽聲觀
<lb ed="X" n="0705b16"/>色總如如。逆順同歸無不可。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b1701">問。性德本有。為甚麼不覺不知。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b1713" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。幾乎忘&CB00230;。</p><p id="pX67p0705b1718" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0705b18"/>幾乎忘&CB00230;。為渠酬酢。方寸靈明。豈從天爵。任麼會
<lb ed="X" n="0705b19"/>去。千錯萬錯。要不錯。休強續鳧來截&CB15112;。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b20"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b2001">問。情惑本空。為甚麼隨聲逐色。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b2013" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。通方衲子。</p><p id="pX67p0705b2018" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0705b21"/>通方衲子果英靈。眼耳無妨信視聽。皓月豈離秋
<lb ed="X" n="0705b22"/>水碧。浮雲那礙曉峰青。聲色堙C&CB15213;還醒。六國安然
<lb ed="X" n="0705b23"/>本自寧。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705b24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705b2401">問。比丘依四念處住。大闡提人依甚麼處住。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705b2418" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。無
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0705c" n="0705c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c01"/>間道中。</p><p id="pX67p0705c0104" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。無間道中。自西自東。快活不徹。受用無
<lb ed="X" n="0705c02"/>窮。君不見提婆達多曾有語。三禪天樂竟非同。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c03"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705c0301">問。大乘與小乘還有相違也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705c0313" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。一有多種。</p><p id="pX67p0705c0318" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0705c04"/>一有多種。群峰勢聳。摩漢凌空。須彌慚悚。吹毛他
<lb ed="X" n="0705c05"/>日當權。應剪人間繁冗。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705c0601">問。真心與妄心還有相順也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705c0613" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。二無兩段。</p><p id="pX67p0705c0618" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0705c07"/>二無兩段。非敢相謾。如如妙智。猶珠走盤。但若圓
<lb ed="X" n="0705c08"/>成一念。休尋萬緒千端。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705c0901">問。三細六麤如何揀擇。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705c0910" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。不曾曳露布。</p><p id="pX67p0705c0916" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。不曾
<lb ed="X" n="0705c10"/>曳露布。業轉現等皆分付。此義文長別日宣。且隨
<lb ed="X" n="0705c11"/>禪苑生機路。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705c1201">問。千差萬別如何融會。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705c1210" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。展開兩手。</p><p id="pX67p0705c1215" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。展開兩
<lb ed="X" n="0705c13"/>手。了無所有。暮四朝三。徒成過咎。要知融會緣由。
<lb ed="X" n="0705c14"/>冬後逐年數九。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705c1501">問。&CB00594;起一指云。俱胝和尚向這堜韙j光明。轉大法
<lb ed="X" n="0705c16"/>輪。諸人還見麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705c1607" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。&CB05232;瞎。</p><p id="pX67p0705c1610" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB05232;瞎那知眼倍明。微
<lb ed="X" n="0705c17"/>塵經卷了平生。指頭尖上些兒箇。消得阿師幾日
<lb ed="X" n="0705c18"/>程。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c19"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705c1901">問。折&CB00560;鐺兒為活計。穿心&CB00179;子作生涯。通玄庵內安
<lb ed="X" n="0705c20"/>然坐。不管山前事似麻。且道安然底是甚麼人。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705c2019" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0705c21"/>無功受祿漢。</p><p id="pX67p0705c2106" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。無功受祿漢。月為鄰兮雲作伴。飢
<lb ed="X" n="0705c22"/>&CB00290;渴飲困時眠。此外不消閑讚嘆。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c23"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0705c2301">問。無求乃樂。為甚麼善遊太子求珠。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0705c2315" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。禍出私門。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0705c24"/><p id="pX67p0705c2401" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。禍出私門自偶然。莫於情識妄鑽研。白雲橫谷
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1312.0706a" n="0706a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706a01"/>舒還卷。豈礙晴空與湛天<note place="inline">此第二十問因前遺失故補於此</note>。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0706a02"/>
